Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.10,0:03:38.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是烩饭炸鸡NO.1比较好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.02,0:03:42.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 没Dr.Pepper啊
